title: Embrace UK Community Support Centre (Embrace UK) secures contract for Social work services without accommodation
body:
United Kingdom, Oct. 15 -- Contract Id: 1746576

Description: United Kingdom based Embrace UK Community Support Centre (Embrace UK) has secured contract 
from London Borough of Haringey for Social work services without accommodation.

The amount of contract is not disclosed.

Country: United Kingdom

Sector: Industry

Contract awarded to Embrace UK Community Support Centre (Embrace UK) Selby Centre Tottenham N17 8JL 
United Kingdom

Contract awarded to executing agency: London Borough of Haringey Level 6 Wood Green N22 8LE United 
Kingdom Contact person: Lisa Bliss E-mail: lisa.bliss@haringey.gov.uk
